reviews.text: I am pretty old school - just 'tahan' the pain and all will be well. So you can imagine, a visit to the dentist is not a pleasant experience. From the reception's warm interior, to the bite block & red-tinted glasses, all of these offered a nice level of comfort for their patients. I am glad I took a leap of faith to try them out.
